{"word":"G2643 - καταλλαγή - katallagḗ - kat-al-lag-ay' - Atonement","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλλαγή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>katallagḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kat-al-lag-ay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Atonement"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஒப்புரவாகுதல் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. exchange; of the business of money - changers, exchanging equivalent values"},{"paragraph":"2. adjustment of a difference, reconciliation, restoration to favor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2644 - καταλλάσσω - katallássō - kat-al-las'-so/2644\">G2644</a>; <i>exchange</i> (figuratively <i>adjustment</i>), that is, <i>restoration</i> to (the divine) favor: - atonement, reconciliation (-ing)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1259 - διαλλάσσω - diallássō - dee-al-las'-so/1259\">G1259</a>, <a href=\"#/G236 - ἀλλάσσω - allássō - al-las'-so/236\">G236</a>, <a href=\"#/G2643 - καταλλαγή - katallagḗ - kat-al-lag-ay'/2643\">G2643</a>, <a href=\"#/G2644 - καταλλάσσω - katallássō - kat-al-las'-so/2644\">G2644</a>, <a href=\"#/G3337 - μεταλλάσσω - metallássō - met-al-las'-so/3337\">G3337</a>, <a href=\"#/G465 - ἀντάλλαγμα - antállagma - an-tal'-ag-mah/465\">G465</a>, <a href=\"#/G525 - ἀπαλλάσσω - apallássō - ap-al-las'-so/525\">G525</a>, <a href=\"#/G604 - ἀποκαταλλάσσω - apokatallássō - ap-ok-at-al-las'-so/604\">G604</a>"}]}